snippet.title: 100% Orange Juice Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
100% Orange Juice is an online board game by Orange Juice, published by Fruitbat Factory.

http://store.steampowered.com/app/282800

Characters from SUGURI, Flying Red Barrel: A Diary of Little Aviator, QP Shooting, Xmas Shooting and Sora come together with all-new characters to duke it out in 100% Orange Juice.

Available in English and Japanese.
http://fruitbatfactory.com
